{"tid":2359915,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"潘兆初獲委任為司法人員推薦委員會委員","createTime":"2021-01-09T09:25:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T10:49:38.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"69da18f1a1b7515c37afb9525c64d3f161f2dcdc","tid":2359915,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:25:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210108/424242622912008192587432.jpeg/6rpf0Lql-k97KdRoNjOcim_lSfom8HWoRW_k9EVv5PQ?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210108%2F424242622912008192587432.jpeg%2F6rpf0Lql-k97KdRoNjOcim_lSfom8HWoRW_k9EVv5PQ%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=72744bdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府宣布，行政長官林鄭月娥已委任高等法院首席法官潘兆初，擔任司法人員推薦委員會委員，任期由2021年1月11日至2022年6月30日。<br />\n<br />\n委員會的職能是就司法職位空缺的填補、司法人員就服務條件提出並經由行政長官轉介予委員會的申述，以及影響司法人員而可予訂明或可由行政長官轉介予委員會的任何事項，向行政長官提供意見或作出推薦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202101/08/P2021010800300.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F202101%2F08%2FP2021010800300.htm&d=M%2BQ4vsyFJ%2Bls%2BsYkNkBEXd5VMZmAwfp0CD4JwUII9h4%3D&h=5b76cb3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/202101/08/P2021010800300.htm</a>"},{"pid":"1ddc481e37be66db4ca17e302d37711def00fa52","tid":2359915,"uid":25468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:46:47.000Z","msg":"佢番去講鬼故算啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8d45419e338a195cd4755d40a46b6050f8a5048","tid":2359915,"uid":179718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-09T09:49:06.000Z","msg":"潘書記<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /